  }

bool isPowerOfFour ( unsigned int n ) {			      def isPowerOfFour ( n ) :					    def is_power_of_four ( n ) :				  failure : #Results: 5, 10
  int count = 0 ;					      	  count = 0						    	count = 0						  
  if ( n && ! ( n & ( n - 1 ) ) ) {			      	  if ( n and ( not ( n & ( n - 1 ) ) ) ) :		    	if n and not ( n & ( n - 1 ) ) :			  
    while ( n > 1 ) {					      	      while ( n > 1 ) :					    	    while n > 1 :					  
      n >>= 1 ;						      		  n >>= 1					    		n >>= 1						  
      count += 1 ;					      		  count += 1					    		count += 1					  
    }							      	      if ( count % 2 == 0 ) :				    	    return ( 1 if count % 2 == 0 else 0 )		  
    return ( count % 2 == 0 ) ? 1 : 0 ;			      		  return True					    	return 0						  
  }							      	      else :						    								  
  return 0 ;						      		  return False					    								  
}

int nCrModp ( int n , int r , int p ) {			      def nCrModp ( n , r , p ) :				    def n_crModp ( n , r , p ) :				  success : None
  int C [ r + 1 ] ;					      	  C = [ 0 for i in range ( r + 1 ) ]			    	C = [ 0 ] * ( r + 1 )					  
  memset ( C , 0 , sizeof ( C ) ) ;			      	  C [ 0 ] = 1						    	C [ 0 ] = 1						  
  C [ 0 ] = 1 ;						      	  for i in range ( 1 , n + 1 ) :			    	for i in range ( 1 , n + 1 ) :				  
  for ( int i = 1 ;					      	      for j in range ( min ( i , r ) , 0 , - 1 ) :	    	    for j in range ( min ( i , r ) , 0 , - 1 ) :	  
  i <= n ;						      		  C [ j ] = ( C [ j ] + C [ j - 1 ] ) % p	    		C [ j ] = ( C [ j ] + C [ j - 1 ] ) % p		  
  i ++ ) {						      	  return C [ r ]					    	return C [ r ]						  
    for ( int j = min ( i , r ) ;			      								    								  
    j > 0 ;						      								    								  
    j -- ) C [ j ] = ( C [ j ] + C [ j - 1 ] ) % p ;	      								    								  
  }							      								    								  
  return C [ r ] ;					      								    								  
}

      count += 1 ;					      	      else :						    	    else :

    }							      		  min_count = min ( min_count , count )		    		min_count = min ( min_count , count )

void printRepeating ( int arr [ ] , int size ) {	      def printRepeating ( arr , size ) :			    def print_repeating ( arr , size ) :			  script_not_found : None
  int Xor = arr [ 0 ] ;					      	  xor = arr [ 0 ]					    	Xor = arr [ 0 ]

int findRepeatingNumber ( const int arr [ ] , int n ) {	      def findRepeatingNumber ( arr , n ) :			    def find_repeating_number ( arr , n ) :			  script_not_found : None

      i -- ;						      		  i -= 1					    		i -= 1

    cout << "Solution doesn't exist!\n" ;		      								    								  
    return ;						      								    								  
  }							      								    								  
}

void luDecomposition ( int mat [ ] [ MAX ] , int n ) {	      def luDecomposition ( mat , n ) :				    def luDecomposition ( mat , n ) :				  script_not_found : None
  int lower [ n ] [ n ] , upper [ n ] [ n ] ;		      	  lower = [ [ 0 for x in range ( n ) ] for y in range ( n ) 	lower , upper = [ 0 ] * n , [ 0 ] * n			  
  memset ( lower , 0 , sizeof ( lower ) ) ;		      	  upper = [ [ 0 for x in range ( n ) ] for y in range ( n ) 	for i in range ( n ) :					  
  memset ( upper , 0 , sizeof ( upper ) ) ;		      	  for i in range ( n ) :				    	    for k in range ( i , n ) :				  
  for ( int i = 0 ;					      	      for k in range ( i , n ) :			    		sum = 0						  
  i < n ;						      		  sum = 0					    		for j in range ( i ) :				  
  i ++ ) {						      		  for j in range ( i ) :			    		    sum += ( lower [ i ] [ j ] * upper [ j ] [ k  
    for ( int k = i ;					      		      sum += ( lower [ i ] [ j ] * upper [ j ] [ k  		upper [ i ] [ k ] = mat [ i ] [ k ] - sum	  
    k < n ;						      		  upper [ i ] [ k ] = mat [ i ] [ k ] - sum	    	    for k in range ( i , n ) :				  
    k ++ ) {						      	      for k in range ( i , n ) :			    		if i == k :					  
      int sum = 0 ;					      		  if ( i == k ) :				    		    lower [ i ] [ i ] = 1			  
      for ( int j = 0 ;					      		      lower [ i ] [ i ] = 1			    		else :						  
      j < i ;						      		  else :					    		    sum = 0					  
      j ++ ) sum += ( lower [ i ] [ j ] * upper [ j ] [ k ] ) 		      sum = 0					    		    for j in range ( i ) :			  
      upper [ i ] [ k ] = mat [ i ] [ k ] - sum ;	      		      for j in range ( i ) :			    			sum += ( lower [ k ] [ j ] * upper [ j ]  
    }							      			  sum += ( lower [ k ] [ j ] * upper [ j ]  		    lower [ k ] [ i ] = ( mat [ k ] [ i ] - sum ) 
    for ( int k = i ;					      		      lower [ k ] [ i ] = int ( ( mat [ k ] [ i ] - 	print ( str ( n ) + "	   Lower Triangular" + str ( n )  
    k < n ;						      	  print ( "Lower Triangular\t\tUpper Triangular" )	    	for i in range ( n ) :					  
    k ++ ) {						      	  for i in range ( n ) :				    	    for j in range ( n ) :
